  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
Lao Tan said, "Why don't you just make him see that life and death are
the same story, that acceptable and unacceptable are on a single
string? Wouldn't it be well to free him from his handcuffs and
fetters?"
